## Usage

/moo [text message] [eyes] [tongue]

Sending:
/moo yoyoyo

Gives:
 ________
< yoyoyo >
 --------
        \   ^__^
         \  (oo)\_______
            (__)\       )\/\
                ||----w |
                ||     ||

You can also use `eyes` and `tongue` parameters to customize your moo even more:

/moo iâ€™m very confmoosed [eyes Oo]

Gives:

 ______________________
< i'm very confmoosed  >
 ----------------------
        \   ^__^
         \  (Oo)\_______
            (__)\       )\/\
                ||----w |
                ||     ||


/moo i like to show my tongue [tongue U] [eyes **]

Gives :
 ____________________________
< i like to show my tongue  >
 ----------------------------
        \   ^__^
         \  (**)\_______
            (__)\       )\/\
             U ||----w |
                ||     ||